name: The Bike List
overview:
The Bike List is a simple site, created by a few UK based cycling enthusiasts ranging from complete novice to the downhill enthusiast. We appreciate how vast and confusing the bike world can be, from when you first dip a toe into the water to your search for that all important upgrade.

Using The Bike List puts you in control of all the bikes available in the UK right now, allowing you to quickly select the best ones for your needs. We don’t sell bikes ourselves, however you can compare all the current deals to find the cheapest, most suitable place to buy your bike, be it from your local dealer or an online store.
